{
  "stem": "26022.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was part-- you'll find religion as one of the subjects in which we were graded.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was part of the general school program.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you left that school in '39, did you say?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I graduated in 1931.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At age 18 and went to the university.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those were relatively quiet days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were actually very-- years-- and went on to study philosophy at the main--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "University of Vienna, Wien Universitat, which is some 700 years old and very prestigious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I worked in the laboratories, studying chemistry, for which I was not very well-suited.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, in retrospect, I must say fortunately, I was sickly at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was a big, strong girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I got all kinds of maladies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I had to stop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the colleagues from my first semester, of course, they went on and on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by the time I got back, they were up there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I felt very left out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was also not very ambitious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I finally was able to convince my father that maybe that was not the career for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I had registered long enough to get a piece of paper, which, in Austria, would be meaningless.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I figured any piece of paper would be valuable when I come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So in '39, I went back and got the Absolutorium.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "All it says-- all it means was that you have registered long enough to graduate if you had done your exams and had written your thesis and had finished your studies.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But that, it doesn't say on the paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I can show you, Absolutorium from the Vienna University.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
